# rvnu — Netlify routing
# Clean URLs that hide the .html extension and surface the bilingual + brand
# pages at the paths people will actually type / share.

# The site root ("/") now serves the temporary holding page (index.html).
# The full bilingual site is preserved and still reachable at /en, /ar, /brand.

# Bilingual entry points (full site lives at home.html now that "/" is the holding page)
/en              /home.html       200
/ar              /ar.html         200

# Brand styleguide (so we can share /brand instead of /brand.html)
/brand           /brand.html      200

# Tolerate trailing-slash and .html-suffix variants
/en/             /home.html       200
/ar/             /ar.html         200
/brand/          /brand.html      200
/home.html       /en              301
/brand.html      /brand           301

# Brand kit downloads — short aliases for the long canonical filenames
/brand/guidelines.pdf      /brand/rvnu-visual-identity-2026.pdf  200
/brand/identity.pdf        /brand/rvnu-visual-identity-2026.pdf  200
